11
00:00:49,410 --> 00:00:53,187
All the PrimeFaces components have been migrated to work with Angular,

12
00:00:53,187 --> 00:00:58,985
so PrimeNG is one of the richest component libraries at the moment

13
00:00:58,985 --> 00:01:03,683
