15
00:01:09,790 --> 00:01:13,598
Bootstrap is a free and open source front-end web framework

16
00:01:13,598 --> 00:01:16,628
for designing websites and web applications.

17
00:01:16,628 --> 00:01:21,261
It contains HTML and CSS based design templates,

18
00:01:21,261 --> 00:01:26,974
but also forms patterns, navigation, and other graphical components.

19
